    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't you just hate doing things? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So do we. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Oops! You’re the Hero!</i> is a story-centered, top-down fantasy adventure game that focuses on a Thief who has stolen a powerful artifact, and decided he doesn’t want to deal with the problems that it brings to him. He journeys across the land to return it, facing and fighting monsters who have deemed him ‘The Hero’, and must destroy him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who are you meant to be? A Hero? Or just someone who deals with responsibilities? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While this game is still a demo, here's a taste of what's in it:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>The Beginning of the Adventure</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An introduction to the story - Who you are! What your purpose is! How much you don't like that! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166160/extras/10e36d0445bfd5063568f4b1c55efe71.poster.avif?t=1771906543\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166160/extras/10e36d0445bfd5063568f4b1c55efe71.webm?t=1771906543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>A Taste of the World You Inhabit </u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're not the only weird thing in the world of Othaya. Why not take a look around and see what you find?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166160/extras/f753098338b5ffd8c7a1161df6d7e686.poster.avif?t=1771906543\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166160/extras/f753098338b5ffd8c7a1161df6d7e686.webm?t=1771906543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166160/extras/f753098338b5ffd8c7a1161df6d7e686.mp4?t=1771906543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Baby's First Fights</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It wouldn't be an adventure without some action. Test your skills with the first bits of combat </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166160/extras/b49f9a85e4ced80f65805649f28fcaee.poster.avif?t=1771906543\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166160/extras/b49f9a85e4ced80f65805649f28fcaee.webm?t=1771906543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166160/extras/b49f9a85e4ced80f65805649f28fcaee.mp4?t=1771906543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All this is yours to test in the <i>Oops! You’re the Hero!</i> Demo, out now!</p>",
